Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT * FROM (
                            SELECT CAST(A.F10003 AS INT) AS "Marca",A.F10017 AS "CNP",A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009 AS "NumeComplet",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie",F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00506 AS "Sectie",I.F00607 AS "Departament", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN '#ffff8000' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN '#dc96dc' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN '#ffffffc8' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN '#FF0066FF' ELSE '#ffc8ffc8' END END) ELSE '#ffffc8c8' END) END END AS "Culoare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN 'Candidat' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN 'Angajat in avans' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= F100923 AND GETDATE() <= F100924) THEN 'Activ suspendat' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= A.F100916) THEN 'Activ detasat' ELSE 'Activ' END END) ELSE 'Inactiv' END) END END AS "Stare",
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10083,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Str. ' + a.F10083 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10084,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Nr. ' + a.F10084 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10085,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Bloc. ' + a.F10085 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100892,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Sc. ' + a.F100892 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100893,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Et. ' + a.F100893 END) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100897 is null or a.F100897 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when niv3.tip in (11, 19, 22, 23) then ' sat ' + niv3.denloc else
                            case when niv3.tip = 6 and upper(niv3.denloc) not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' + niv3.DENLOC else ' ' + niv3.denloc end END end) +

                            (case when a.F100914 is null or a.F100914 = 0 THEN '' else case when niv2.tip in (1, 4) and UPPER(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + niv2.DENLOC else
                            case when niv2.tip = 2 and UPPER(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%ORAS%' then ' orasul ' + niv2.DENLOC else 
                            case when niv2.TIP = 3 and upper(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' + niv2.DENLOC else ' ' + niv2.denloc end end end end ) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100921 is null or a.F100921 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%JUDET%' or upper(niv1.denloc)  like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' ' + niv1.DENLOC else
                             case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%BUCURESTI%' then ' municipiul ' + niv1.DENLOC else ' judetul ' + niv1.denloc end end END) +
                            

                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10087,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Cod Postal. ' + a.F10087 END) AS "AdresaCompleta"
                             
                            FROM F100 A
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202 
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304 
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405 
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506 
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607 
                            left join Localitati niv1 on niv1.SIRUTA = a.F100921
                            left join Localitati niv2 on niv2.SIRUTA = a.F100914
                            left join Localitati niv3 on niv3.SIRUTA = a.F100897
                             
                            WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN (SELECT CAST(F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM USERS WHERE F70102 = 5
                            UNION
                            SELECT B.F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE C."IdSuper" = 5  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 )
                            UNION
                            SELECT CAST(B.F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" D ON B.F10003=D.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = -1 * D."IdSuper"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE D."IdUser" = 5  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 ))
                            ) X WHERE 1=1  AND ( "Stare"='Activ' OR  "Stare"='Angajat in avans')
                            ORDER BY "NumeComplet"

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=3) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 3) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 3  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 3 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  3))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=3 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE

				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"

								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003"

		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"

	                                    end, -99)

                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99))

		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 253) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 253  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=253 AND 253 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  253))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != 253)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User",

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",

	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 253),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=253),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=253),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=253) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 253) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 253  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=253 AND 253 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"

								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"

                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003"

		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1

                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz",

                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=253 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=253 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=253 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",

					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F17 = (
select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=23 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=2020 and Luna=2 and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = 23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;
UPDATE "Ptj_Cumulat" SET F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=2020 AND MONTH(Ziua)=2 AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=23) WHERE F10003=23 AND "An"=2020 AND "Luna"=2;

END;

Pagina:    General

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"

                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
