						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"

	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003

                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X WHERE Stare NOT LIKE '%finalizat%') X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"

							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT * FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",
	                chest."DataInceput", chest."DataSfarsit", isnull(fnume."F10009", '') + ' ' + isnull(fnume."F10008", '') as "Utilizator",
	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")

																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")

																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN B.F10003 IS NULL THEN B.F70104 ELSE E.F10008 + ' ' + E.F10009 END AS "User", 
                        C.F10008 + ' ' + C.F10009 AS "Evaluat", D."Denumire" AS "Quiz", 
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",
                        A.*
                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A
                        INNER JOIN USERS B ON A."IdUser"=B.F70102
                        LEFT JOIN F100 E ON B.F10003=E.F10003
                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003
                        INNER JOIN "Eval_Quiz" D ON A."IdQuiz"=D."Id"
                        WHERE (A."IdUser"=2 OR A.F10003=-99)) X

				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case
											                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) > 0 then 'Evaluare ' + usSuper."F70104"
											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",
	                case
		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")
				                else case
						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case
										                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 5 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5_2")
										                else case 
												                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 6 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super6_2")
												                else case
														                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 7 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super7_2")
														                else case
																                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 8 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super8_2")
																                else
																	                case 
																		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 9 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super9_2")
																		                else convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super10_2")
																	                end
															                end
													                 end
											                 end
									                end
							                end
					                end
			                end
	                end as "Observatii",
	                case 
		                when rasp."Pozitie" = ist."Pozitie" then 1
                        when  ctg."Id" != 0   then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "PoateModifica",
	                case 
		                when isnull(chest."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else chest."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "TrebuieSaIaLaCunostinta",
	                case
		                when isnull(rasp."LuatLaCunostinta", -99) = -99 then 0
		                else rasp."LuatLaCunostinta"
	                end as "ALuatLaCunostinta",
	                /*ist."IdSuper" as "RolulMeu",*/
	                case
		                when isnull(dr."PozitieVizibila", -99) = 0  then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "FaraDrepturi", per."DenPerioada",
                CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" Z WHERE Z."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2) <> 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Quiz360Completat"
                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"
									                and rasLinii."TipData" = 16
                left join "Eval_Drepturi" dr on ist."IdQuiz" = dr."IdQuiz"
						                and ist."Pozitie" = dr."Pozitie"
						                and 0 = dr."PozitieVizibila"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist1 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist1."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist1."F10003"
								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist4."F10003"
								                and 4 = ist4."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist5 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist5."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist5."F10003"
								                and 5 = ist5."Pozitie"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_Perioada" per ON chest."Anul" = per."IdPerioada"
                where rasp."IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" 
                and rasp."F10003" = rasp."F10003" 
                and isnull(case 
		                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                    end, -99)  = isnull(case 
		                                    when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                                    else dr."Pozitie"
	                                    end, -99)
                and isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99)  = isnull(ist."IdSuper", -99) AND (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and ist."IdUser" =  2))
                and fnume.F10025 in (0, 999)

                and (ctg."Id" = 0 OR (ctg."Id" != 0  and rasp.F10003 != -99)) 
                ) X

                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Invitat de catre mine' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=1 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu sunt invitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A.F10003=-99 THEN 'Coleg autoinvitat' ELSE
                        CASE WHEN A."IdTip"=2 AND A."IdUser"=2 THEN 'Eu dau feedback autoinvitat' ELSE '' END END END END AS "Tip",

                        FROM "Eval_Invitatie360" A

                        INNER JOIN F100 C ON A.F10003=C.F10003

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (
                select distinct rasp."IdAuto", rasp."IdQuiz", rasp."F10003", chest."Denumire", ctg."Denumire" AS "DenumireCategorie", chest."CategorieQuiz",

	                CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz" = rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser" = 2),0)=1 THEN '#FFE18030' ELSE '#FFFFFF00' END AS "Culoare",
	                case
                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE

			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'

						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'

											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end

			                      end

		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")
				                else case
						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")
						                else case
								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")
								                else case
										                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist1."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1")
										                else ''
									                end
							                end
					                  end
			                  end
	                end as "Rating",

		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")

						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")

                from "Eval_Raspuns" rasp
                join "Eval_Quiz" chest on rasp."IdQuiz" = chest."Id"
                join "F100" fnume on rasp."F10003" = fnume."F10003"
                LEFT JOIN "Eval_tblCategorie" ctg ON chest."CategorieQuiz"=ctg."Id"
                 INNER  join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist."IdQuiz"
							                and rasp."F10003" = ist."F10003" AND (ist."IdUser" = 2  OR (ist."Pozitie"=1 AND ctg."Id" = 0 AND rasp.F10003=-99 AND 2 NOT IN (SELECT XX.IdUSer FROM Eval_RaspunsIStoric XX WHERE XX.F10003=ist.F10003 AND XX.IdQuiz=ist.IdQuiz)))
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" istPoz on rasp."IdQuiz" = istPoz."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = istPoz."F10003"
									                and rasp."Pozitie" = istPoz."Pozitie"
                left join "tblSupervizori" super on (-1 * istPoz."IdSuper") = super."Id"
                left join USERS usSuper on istPoz."IdUser" = usSuper."F70102"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsLinii" rasLinii on rasp."IdQuiz" = rasLinii."IdQuiz"
									                and rasp."F10003" = rasLinii."F10003"

								                and 1 = ist1."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist2 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist2."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist2."F10003"
								                and 2 = ist2."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist3 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist3."IdQuiz"
								                and rasp."F10003" = ist3."F10003"
								                and 3 = ist3."Pozitie"
                left join "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" ist4 on rasp."IdQuiz" = ist4."IdQuiz"

Eroarea:   SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (

                        when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 2 then 'Contestat'
		                when rasp."LuatLaCunostinta" = 1 then 'Luat la cunostinta'
		                else 
						    CASE 
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare 360' END)
						    WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=2 THEN (CASE WHEN COALESCE((SELECT MIN(COALESCE("Aprobat",0)) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2),0) = 1 THEN 'Finalizat' ELSE 'Evaluare pe proiect' END)
						    ELSE
                                case
			                         when rasp."Finalizat" = 1 then 'Evaluare finalizata'
				                     else case 
						                      when convert(date, getdate()) not between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 'Evaluare expirata'
						                      else CASE WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=1 THEN 'Evaluare 360' ELSE
                                                   case
									                    when isnull(istPoz."IdSuper", -99) = 0 then 'Evaluare angajat'
									                    else case

											                    else super."Alias"
										                     end
							                       end
                                                END
					                      end
			                      end
                        END
	                end as "Stare",
	                case 
		                when dr."PozitieVizibila" = 0 then 1
		                else dr."Pozitie"
	                end as "Pozitie",
                    rasp."Pozitie" as "PozitiePeCircuit",
	                /*ist."IdSuper",*/
                    CASE   WHEN COALESCE(chest."CategorieQuiz",0)=0 THEN rasp."Finalizat" ELSE (SELECT COALESCE("Aprobat",0) FROM "Eval_RaspunsIstoric" WHERE F10003=rasp.F10003 and "IdQuiz"=rasp."IdQuiz" AND "IdUser"=2) END AS "Finalizat",                     
                    /*rasp."Finalizat",*/
	                case
		                when convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, chest."DataInceput") and convert(date, chest."DataSfarsit") then 1
		                else 0
	                end as "Expirat",
	                isnull(ist."Aprobat", 0) as "Aprobat",
	                case 
		                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist5."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super5")
		                else case
				                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist4."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4")

						                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist3."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3")

								                when isnull(convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2"), -99) <> -99 and isnull(convert(varchar, ist2."Aprobat"), -99) = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2")

			                  end

		                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 1 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super1_2")
		                else case
				                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 2 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super2_2")

						                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 3 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super3_2")
						                else case 
								                when convert(varchar, ist."Pozitie") = 4 then convert(varchar, rasLinii."Super4_2")
								                else case

		                        left join SituatieZileAbsente zabs on zabs.F10003 = x.F10003 and zabs.An = x.An and zabs.IdAbsenta = (select Id from Ptj_tblAbsente where DenumireScurta = 'CO')
		                        left join SituatieZLP zlp on zlp.F10003 = x.F10003 and zlp.An = x.An
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2020-02-01] AS "Ziua1", [2020-02-02] AS "Ziua2", [2020-02-03] AS "Ziua3", [2020-02-04] AS "Ziua4", [2020-02-05] AS "Ziua5", [2020-02-06] AS "Ziua6", [2020-02-07] AS "Ziua7", [2020-02-08] AS "Ziua8", [2020-02-09] AS "Ziua9", [2020-02-10] AS "Ziua10", [2020-02-11] AS "Ziua11", [2020-02-12] AS "Ziua12", [2020-02-13] AS "Ziua13", [2020-02-14] AS "Ziua14", [2020-02-15] AS "Ziua15", [2020-02-16] AS "Ziua16", [2020-02-17] AS "Ziua17", [2020-02-18] AS "Ziua18", [2020-02-19] AS "Ziua19", [2020-02-20] AS "Ziua20", [2020-02-21] AS "Ziua21", [2020-02-22] AS "Ziua22", [2020-02-23] AS "Ziua23", [2020-02-24] AS "Ziua24", [2020-02-25] AS "Ziua25", [2020-02-26] AS "Ziua26", [2020-02-27] AS "Ziua27", [2020-02-28] AS "Ziua28", [2020-02-29] AS "Ziua29" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, "ValStr", "Ziua" FROM "Ptj_Intrari_2" WHERE '2020-02-01' <= CAST("Ziua" AS date) AND CAST("Ziua" AS date) <= '2020-02-29') source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX("ValStr") FOR "Ziua" IN (  [2020-02-01], [2020-02-02], [2020-02-03], [2020-02-04], [2020-02-05], [2020-02-06], [2020-02-07], [2020-02-08], [2020-02-09], [2020-02-10], [2020-02-11], [2020-02-12], [2020-02-13], [2020-02-14], [2020-02-15], [2020-02-16], [2020-02-17], [2020-02-18], [2020-02-19], [2020-02-20], [2020-02-21], [2020-02-22], [2020-02-23], [2020-02-24], [2020-02-25], [2020-02-26], [2020-02-27], [2020-02-28], [2020-02-29] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                
                                
                                
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2020-02-01] AS "CuloareValoare1", [2020-02-02] AS "CuloareValoare2", [2020-02-03] AS "CuloareValoare3", [2020-02-04] AS "CuloareValoare4", [2020-02-05] AS "CuloareValoare5", [2020-02-06] AS "CuloareValoare6", [2020-02-07] AS "CuloareValoare7", [2020-02-08] AS "CuloareValoare8", [2020-02-09] AS "CuloareValoare9", [2020-02-10] AS "CuloareValoare10", [2020-02-11] AS "CuloareValoare11", [2020-02-12] AS "CuloareValoare12", [2020-02-13] AS "CuloareValoare13", [2020-02-14] AS "CuloareValoare14", [2020-02-15] AS "CuloareValoare15", [2020-02-16] AS "CuloareValoare16", [2020-02-17] AS "CuloareValoare17", [2020-02-18] AS "CuloareValoare18", [2020-02-19] AS "CuloareValoare19", [2020-02-20] AS "CuloareValoare20", [2020-02-21] AS "CuloareValoare21", [2020-02-22] AS "CuloareValoare22", [2020-02-23] AS "CuloareValoare23", [2020-02-24] AS "CuloareValoare24", [2020-02-25] AS "CuloareValoare25", [2020-02-26] AS "CuloareValoare26", [2020-02-27] AS "CuloareValoare27", [2020-02-28] AS "CuloareValoare28", [2020-02-29] AS "CuloareValoare29" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, "CuloareValoare", "Ziua" From "Ptj_Intrari_2" WHERE '2020-02-01' <= CAST("Ziua" AS date) AND CAST("Ziua" AS date) <= '2020-02-29') source  
                                PIVOT (MAX("CuloareValoare") FOR "Ziua" IN (  [2020-02-01], [2020-02-02], [2020-02-03], [2020-02-04], [2020-02-05], [2020-02-06], [2020-02-07], [2020-02-08], [2020-02-09], [2020-02-10], [2020-02-11], [2020-02-12], [2020-02-13], [2020-02-14], [2020-02-15], [2020-02-16], [2020-02-17], [2020-02-18], [2020-02-19], [2020-02-20], [2020-02-21], [2020-02-22], [2020-02-23], [2020-02-24], [2020-02-25], [2020-02-26], [2020-02-27], [2020-02-28], [2020-02-29] )) pvt
                                ) pvtCuloare ON X.F10003=pvtCuloare.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN F1001 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2020 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 2 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                 LEFT JOIN "viewCategoriePontaj" CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2020-02-29') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON B.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON B.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2020 AND X.Luna = 2 
                                ORDER BY NumeComplet) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2020 + 2 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE S.F10025 <> 900 AND CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2020-2-29' AND '2020-2-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)
-----------------------------------------------------
